Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2019,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: Excellent location, very safe area with a park right accross for walks and a small convenience store for urgent needs. Saleh is very responsive and easy to approach. I have to mention that building staff are very warm and helpful. The place itself has good amenities and it was perfect for my month long stay. Very glad i booked it and hope to stay again.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · July 2018,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: The location was perfect for my husband and I. It’s safe and beautiful. There’s a park right across the apartment building. The apartment was cleanly kept. And the host is very responsive whenever we had a problem. The AC broke down and he immediately sent the electrician in a day’s notice.
